<p>
  I think the advent of APIs - for things like twitter, facebook and gmail -
  makes doing personal analytics a lot easier than it was before. We're all
  entrenched, pouring our lives into these platforms. Without realizing it we have created
  a profusion of opportunities to do personal analytics.
</p>

